  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This will make a magical Spear. If someone In your party has a weapon that is not as good as the spear, just whip out a weapon for them to use for battle. If your party is going to fight undead, you can  give it to people in your party who do not have magic weapons.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>None
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
